values: It's been such a long time since I posted something on my lj... I've been really busy with my exams coming in 2 weeks and some other things happening with my life... Well, I changed my layout, something new is always good!!!! *smile* I'm thinking of writing again but it will probably be after my exams, so a little bit more of patience please... *puppy look* I searched for some Kirk materials and I found some "Black Donnellys" videos so enjoy!!!!!!! Poor Nicky! Funny one! And to finish, I found the episode 2 of "The Black Donnellys" Part 1 Part 2 Part 3

I have nothing to say except: Why does Kirk look so young???? It's probably the shirt. Enjoy! Well, it's on the same page, when you click on the 103 commentary, but I've got some problems with that site, it doesn't work with me... GRRRRR Luckily I saw it yesterday!!!

I've found 2 interviews with Kirk!!! One is a video and the other one is an article. And since I'm a very nice girl...*cough* lol, well I thought I could share them with you!!!! *smile* Kirk is talking about his role in 'The Black Donnellys'!! I find him very cute on this one, but I find he's talking weird at the beginning, well it's probably due to the fact that for once he's not muttering under his breath... lol It's a change!!!! And "yeah, GO Kirk, you're so great in the role of the bad guy!!!!" Here is the article!!! Did you see, did you see?????? He's not satisfied with the end of his character in OZ... Who agrees with him?????? ME ME ME LOL

I had found the pilot on Youtube a while ago, but it was deleted since then... But since I try to stay updated with anything regarding my favorites boys, guess what, I've found the episode again Here! He's simply still very attractive in bad guy, don't you think? And when he winks and smiles at a moment, well I was simply smiling like an idiot myself... lol Anyway, enjoy the sexiness!!!! ;) God, he's so yummy on this one...

I watched them a while ago and I thought maybe you'd be interested in watching them too... Well, he hasn't a very big part in it, but Kirk in military suit is just yummy!!! *smile* Anyway enjoy! Episode 1 'currahee': Part 1 Part 2 Episode 2 'day of days': Part 1 Part 2 Episode 4 'replacements': Part 1 Well in this one, he only appears in the first part. Episode 5 'crossroads': Part 2 He's only in the second part, this time. Episode 6 'bastogne': Part 1 Again, he's only in the first part, too bad... Episode 7 'the breaking point': Part 1 Part 2

Well, being sick today didn't help, all day in bed and it was like I couldn't stop sleeping. Do you know that feeling???
Well, I'm not feeling very inspired these days. My muses can't be gone right????
I feel like all M/R fans have disappeared somewhere and I'm all alone.
Where are you damn it???
Well, don't mind my ramblings, it's probably due to my bad mood, but it's hard.
The communities and the groups are dead and the only fics that come out are B/K fics, so unfair...
Well, I don't know what to do, to find my inspiration again... Maybe watching OZ episodes would help... Well, I hope...

... to tell you that I finished my special Valentine's day fic. All I need to do now, is to write it down on my computer. Yeah, I wrote it the old way, paper and pencil...
Well, I'll post it tomorrow, wednesday, probably around noon on my clock.
Stay tuned!!!!!

Well, I've got only one thing to say: Kirk Acevedo is very well proportioned... *blushing* Go here if you want to know what I'm talking about When I was watching the show for the first time, I was waiting impatiently to see a little bit more of Kirk, such a perv right??? And when I saw that, I jumped out of my seat, probably drooling though... lol Anyway, I simply love Kirk's body!!! Another thing, for those who want to watch other clips with Miguel, search for 'Miguel Alvarez' on Youtube, there are some great ones...

If you never saw Kirk in "Kirk and Kerry", you need to watch it right now!!! Kirk is simply (well I can't seem to find the right word), but I'd say one thing: 'WOW' before fainting. lol pointed to me that site where you can download it. It's on the left side of the page, divx or quicktime. Well, I hope you'll enjoy it as much as I did... Don't you think that Kirk with longer hair is simply irresistible?????

Yeah, I found a clip of Dean in the show "30 Rock". He's really cute in this one. The girl is probably nuts, why did she break up with him???? *sigh* Well go check it out, Gimme Dean! Well, it seems it's not available anymore, too bad!!!!

Yeah, here in France, we already are in 2007!!!! What about my new resolution???? Well, writing more Miguel/Ryan hot scenes, how about that?? lol Well, I wish you all the best and blah blah blah... By the way, I found Kirk's second episode on "Third watch" (I didn't find the first though, so it kinda sucks but it's always something I guess...) Here's the link: I want Kirk About the fic, well I don't know when I'm gonna post my new chapter, probably this week...

For those who are interested, there is the first episode of this new TV show on youtube Here! No longer available, sorry... He really doesn't seem to get any older, it's so weird!!! I was inspired by the beginning of the third part to write the end of my fic. Did you notice that wink???? If only it was meant for Ryan...

I was working on my fic until now, but I'm too tired to continue (it's 2AM for me!!!!)
So I'll post my next chapter probably tomorrow...
Anyway, apart from that, I hope you passed a great Christmas. ;)

It's been only two days that I didn't go on the internet and for me, it seems like a week passed... It's so great to be on holidays!!!
I hope you're enjoying yours as well.
About the fic, well, I should write my next chapter after Christmas (at least I hope I'll have the time...)
It's funny cause I know how to finish it, but don't worry, I still have other chapters to write before!!!
More Miguel/Ryan hot scenes, how about that???? lol
Well, now, I'm going to watch Kirk in Law and Order (even if it's in French) and I'll concentrate on him and only on him...
Oh, I'm such a fool!!!

Yeah, it's actually the holidays for me, finally!!! So, I wanted to let you know that it will be probably difficult for me to work on my fic, in the next few days. Yeah, I know it's sad, no, don't cry... lol Anyway, enjoy the chapters I already wrote and don't worry, I intend to continue it, especially now that things sped up between them!! Oh, I almost forgot, made beautiful music videos with Miguel, Ryan and also one with Miguel and Ryan together (Magnifque! by the way). So, check them out!!! Three videos here! Miguel/Ryan one!

I was so busy today that I didn't have the time to work on my fic, but I'll try to write my new chapter tomorrow, I promise. I thought about it again, last night. It obsesses me, I have to write it down soon... So, to make the waiting more bearable, I've got something for you!! I found it some days ago and I think you'll like it... posted Miguel/Kirk and Dean pictures at her lj Pics! The first one kills me, he's such a tease. We all know who that look is for, right?? lol I didn't see it before and I couldn't help watching it at least one time a day. *drooling* So I made an icon of it (the one I used for this entry). The third is nice too, the Miguel stare, yeah!! Anyway, enjoy... ;)

I'm finally in the Christmas spirit!! Yeah, which is why I was in the mood to change the layout of my lj.
Everyone around me was talking about Christmas trees, tinsels, gifts and all, and I was like: 'Why I don't want to celebrate it? It's not normal...'
Anyway, I thought about my fic and I know how to write the first Miguel/Ryan sexual relation. No, no need to applaud!! lol
It's all in my head (I even dreamt of it and I was in a wonderful mood when I woke up...), now I still have to write it. *sigh*
Miguel and Ryan touching... mmmhhh!!   ;)

I was watching this afternoon, two episodes of Law and Order: Trial by Jury with Kirk and I'm kinda disappointed.
I still love to see him on TV, that's not the point, but I'm always expecting him to be like Miguel, but no...
It's silly but it's always like that! 
I saw the episode of Fastlane and the one of Numbers he was in and it's the same thing.
Did I mention the episodes I saw, were in french and Kirk dubbed in french, well, it's totally different... Sometimes I hate beeing french, why they have to dub every shows?? *crying*  lol
Anyway, it's probably the beret, yeah definitely!! I don't think it's so good on him and yet I'm french... Ah la la...

If you want to hear Miguel dubbed in spanish go there: Spanish Miguel! When I played it for the first time, I was expecting it was in english and surprise!! I know that here in France, a long time ago, there were some of the episodes in french but I never saw them. Anyway, I'm glad I saw the show in english, it's hard to imagine Miguel or even Ryan with another voice... It's so weird! By the way, why it's hotter when Kirk talks in spanish than when he's dubbed in spanish?? lol

I was watching again the episode 5 of season 1 and I noticed something funny in the scene with Alvarez and Groves when they're in lockdown.
I always looked deeply at Miguel (I wonder why... lol) in this scene which I find very hot, especially at the end, but this time something caught my attention.
When Groves tells Miguel he likes his scars (who wouldn't?) and just before he moves on his bed, we can actually see a mike at the right bottom of the screen.
I always like to notice these kinds of things, it amuses me. 
Now you probably think I'm silly, right?
